### Login player 1
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "player1",
    "password": "testpass123"
}

### Login player 2
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "player2",
    "password": "testpass123"
