### Create a new lobby (player 1)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/create/test_game/
Authorization: Bearer <player1_token>

### Join lobby (player 2)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/join/test_game/
Authorization: Bearer <player2_token>

### Get lobby info
GET http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/info/test_game/
Authorization: Bearer <player1_token>

### List all lobbies
GET http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/info/
Authorization: Bearer <player1_token>

### Get player status
GET http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/status/
Authorization: Bearer <player1_token>

### Start game (player 1 - creator)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/start/
Authorization: Bearer <player1_token>

### Player actions during game
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/call/
Authorization: Bearer <player1_token>

### 
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/fold/
Authorization: Bearer <player2_token>

### 
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/raise/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <player1_token>

{
    "amount": 50
}

### Leave lobby
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/lobby/leave/
Authorization: Bearer <player1_token>
